sentences: Lars Winther (born February 22, 1983) is a Danish pianist, composer, producer and arranger.

He released the debut-album LIVE_2005 with Lars Winther Trio in 2005, followed by the double-disc CD/DVD Nordic By Nature in 2007 — receiving many positive reviews for the latter, as well as distribution throughout Europe and in parts of Asia.
